data.description: Welcome to Sunburst Townhomes.  Completely redone attached single family ranch home!  3 bed 1 bath end unit with fresh paint inside and outside, renovated kitchen with granite countertops, remodeled bathroom, newly installed and freshly painted door/floor trim, new door hardware & hinges, various USB outlets in key areas and new carpet and flooring throughout.  This is a unique ranch unit with an unshared corner front yard and fenced patio area with oversized, one car attached garage.   New garage door and belt drive, garage door opener.  This attached home has no interior party wall (attached only at the garages).  Low HOA dues!   A true lock and leave property as the HOA takes care of all front and rear lawn care and road maintenance.  Water and sewer are included with the fees and Sunburst Park is within walking distance from your front porch.  One of the most private and quiet lots in the complex!   This unit is located near the rear of this well planned community and backs to single family homes. This location allows for an expandable backyard that can be fenced.. expanding your outdoor living space.  (Architectural review form is in the supplements).  Thermostat activated attic fan keeps the unit cool with two bedroom ceiling fans and new dining area ceiling fan/light with remote.  Schedule your showing today!
data.whatILove: The quiet and private location in Sunburst, expandable backyard, RV lot and attached home at garage only..no interior party wall!  All yard maintenance it done for me through the HOA.  A true lock and leave property.
